Domestic mites are microscopic arachnids that occur in various households microhabitats and are traditionally grouped according to their ecological preferences as house dust mites (
Pyroglyphidae
), and storages mites (
Acaridae
, 
Glycyphagidae
, 
Echimyopodidae
and Chorto- glyphidae (

; 

